The paper also involves linear algebra and statistical theories, indicating a possible connection to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper mentions state-of-the-art Neural Network models, suggesting a possible connection to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
